Package: phazevpn-client
Version: 2.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: PhazeVPN <support@phazevpn.duckdns.org>
Description: PhazeVPN Unified Client & Dashboard
 All-in-one VPN client with integrated dashboard, Tor support,
 and all VPN modes (Normal, Semi Ghost, Full Ghost, Tor Ghost).
 Modern UI matching website design. Automatic updates via APT.
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-requests, python3-tk
Recommends: tor, network-manager-openvpn
Priority: optional
Section: net
Homepage: https://phazevpn.duckdns.org
